{
  "stem": "4693.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Our food was a piece of bread, some tea in the morning, some-- a bit of sugar-- a spoon of sugar-- and some so-called soup in the evening.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know at this time what the charges-- because I was not put-- at this time-- in front of the court, which I actually never was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Another matter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Obviously, the charge was illegal coming through the border.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They started in Poltava, taking us for interviews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] No, this was not in Poltava, this was later in Kremenchuk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After staying in Poltava, I don't remember how long, they put us in these Black Maria [LAUGHS] trucks, and into a train again.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They inherited, from the Czar regime, the special railway cars for prisoners.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were the same cars as what was in Sardy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And, we were transported always inside this, every train had such a car.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were transported in this car, we came to Kremenchuk, which is another town on the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there we found ourselves already in a larger cell with a number of people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And from there, we were starting being taken for interrogations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the system what always won.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You are not permitted to sleep during the day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "During the night, the light was always bright, and we are not permitted to cover ourselves up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So there's a guy who was looking through the spyhole.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we are not there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were taken and started the investigation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a stupid investigations.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were done this way to make you tired.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So they took you, and asked you some stupid questions, and ask you with a couple of guys for a couple of hours.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then they put you into the out-- and say, go back to your cell.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
